name: time
query:
MATCH (issue :ISSUE)-[:SOLVE_BY]->(technician :HUMAN:TECHNICIAN)
MATCH (issue :ISSUE)-[:CONTAINS]->(tag_item :TAG :ITEM)
MATCH (issue :ISSUE)

WHERE technician.name = "lyle cookson"
RETURN tag_item.keyword, issue.date_maintenance_work_order_close, issue.date_maintenance_work_order_issue, count(issue) AS issue_count

name: Lyle_item
query:
MATCH (issue :ISSUE)-[:CONTAINS]->(tag_item :TAG :ITEM)
MATCH (issue :ISSUE)-[:SOLVE_BY]->(technician :HUMAN:TECHNICIAN)

WHERE technician.name = "lyle cookson"
RETURN tag_item.keyword, count(issue) AS issue_count

name: time
query:
MATCH (issue :ISSUE)
MATCH (issue :ISSUE)-[:COVERED]->(machine :MACHINE)

WHERE machine.name = "i1" OR machine.name = "i2"
RETURN issue.date_maintenance_work_order_close, issue.date_maintenance_work_order_issue, machine.name, count(issue) AS issue_count
